{"type": "assistant", "message": {"id": "msg_1783409648313", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "我已经有足够的锚点来进行严谨的审查。关键发现：APSIPA 2025 的论文 \"Fusing Multi-Layer Features of the Pre-Trained Model with Grouped Cross Attention for Spoofing Speech Detection\" 提出了一种用于多层 SSL 特征的 Grouped Cross Attention 模块 —— 这与 MOSAIC 的核心机制有大量重叠。此外，还有 \"Phonetically Explainable Speech Deepfake Detection\" (arXiv 2606.15454, 2026 年 6 月) —— 时间上很接近，可能属于并行研究。ASVspoof 5 (2024) 是目前的挑战赛，但本文仅评估到 2021 年。现在我将撰写最终审查报告。"}], "model": "GLM-5.2-w4a8", "stop_reason": null, "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 0, "output_tokens": 0, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}, "context_management": null}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "44ba316e-6965-4727-aa15-fd655b7132ec", "uuid": "8aef87cb-5699-472c-8ca1-a6a799f4bfec"}
